## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9998-103">根據預設，類別的 Help 關鍵字由指定<xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-103">By default, the Help keyword for a class is given by the <xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f9998-104">對於成員而言，所宣告的屬性，類型的完整名稱加上屬性名稱本身提供的 Help 關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-104">For members, the Help keyword is given by the full name of the type that declared the property, plus the property name itself.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9998-105">例如，請考慮<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性上的<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType>控制項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-105">For example, consider the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f9998-106">Class 關鍵字是 「 System.Windows.Forms.Button"，但<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>property 關鍵字是 「 System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text"，因為<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性宣告上<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=nameWithType>類別，而非<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType>類別本身;<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType>類別繼承屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-106">The class keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Button", but the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text", because the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is declared on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=nameWithType> class, rather than the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> class itself; the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> class inherits the property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9998-107">相反地，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性宣告上<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType>類別中，因此它的關鍵字是 「 System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-107">By contrast, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is declared on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> class, so its keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult".</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9998-108">當 [說明] 系統取得的關鍵字時，它會先查看<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-108">When the Help system gets the keywords, it will first look at <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f9998-109">在類別層級，它會傳回所指定的字串<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-109">At the class level, it will return the string specified by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f9998-110">這不會使用之成員的問題，仍會反映實際完整名稱的宣告型別，以及成員名稱的型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-110">This will not be used for members of the type in question, which will still reflect the declaring type's actual full name, plus the member name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f9998-111">這個屬性會支援具有相關聯的一般文件，但有不同的說明 Id 的強型別的類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-111">This attribute supports strongly typed classes that have associated common documentation but distinct Help IDs.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9998-112">下列程式碼範例示範如何將屬性放上該成員本身，以覆寫此說明系統行為。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-112">The following code example shows how to override this Help system behavior by placing the attribute on the member itself.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f9998-113">這些是針對下列類別，稱為關鍵字`DemoComponent`:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-113">These are the keywords for the following class, called `DemoComponent`:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f9998-114">Class 關鍵字:"`System.ComponentModel.Component`」 (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent`)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-114">Class keyword: "`System.ComponentModel.Component`" (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent`)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f9998-115">Property1 關鍵字: 「`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property1`"（預設值）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-115">Property1 keyword: "`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property1`" (default)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="f9998-116">為 property2 的內容關鍵字:"`SomeNamespace.SomeOtherClass.Property2`」 (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property2`)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-116">Property2 keyword: "`SomeNamespace.SomeOtherClass.Property2`" (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property2`)</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[HelpKeywordAttribute(typeof(Component))]  
public class DemoComponent : Component  
{  
    public string Property1  
    {  
        get  
        {  
            return "";  
        }  
    }  
  
    [HelpKeywordAttribute("SomeNamespace.SomeOtherClass.Property2")]  
    public string Property2  
    {  
        get  
        {  
            return "";  
        }  
    }  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9998-117">下列程式碼範例示範如何使用<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>類別，以指定的內容關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-117">The following code example demonstrates using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute> class to specify a context keyword.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f9998-118">如需這個程式碼範例的完整說明，請參閱 <<c0> [ 如何： 在 Windows Form 控制項中套用屬性](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/how-to-apply-attributes-in-windows-forms-controls.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9998-118">For a complete explanation of this code example, see [How to: Apply Attributes in Windows Forms Controls](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/how-to-apply-attributes-in-windows-forms-controls.md).</span></span>  
  
